se.hig.dvg329.algomaze.control.solvers

Interface MazeSolver

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DijkstraMazeSolver

    public interface MazeSolver
    A MazeSolver takes a Maze as a parameter and returns a Stack containing Cells that comprise the solution to the Maze. A MazeSolver should mark all Cells that are part of the solution with the value Cell.CellValue.SOLUTION using the Cell.setValue(se.hig.dvg329.algomaze.model.Cell.CellValue) method.
